{"id": "1510922341226647634", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "打法展示：", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:25:57.728000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510923255085662218", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "# 小結\n隊友方面 混沌凱最推薦吃萊克拿高體質並且還能抽一下牌(0啟就能用)\n隊伍方面 需要整體比較高的練度 隊友的等級 靈塑 精通以及守秘人的等級", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:29:35.609000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510923885632294934", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "接下來先分享一下海超 再補凱的配置要求", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:32:05.943000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510923916632264774", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "# 海超特性", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:32:13.334000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510924203883368579", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "由於是混界域的關係 精通收益會下降\n所以這邊建議生存就交給隊友\n隊伍去叠強效 強效建議100以上", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:33:21.820000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:48:03.688000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510926127382794342", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "# 隊伍配置\n這邊就不寫超維角色體質三圍了", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:41:00.418000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:43:51.256000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510926416240443402", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "我建議配鳥哥(卡斯托爾)跟溫柯爾\n鳥哥0啟就可以 溫沒有+4可以考慮用其他的", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:42:09.287000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:48:59.591000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510927070816112680", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "剩下那個隨便選 這邊選到的是艾瑞卡\n因為其銀鑰屬性以及不俗的體質", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:44:45.350000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510928733438083173", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "這邊是沒有考慮阿拉克涅跟奧爾拉的\n有會更好 但是性價比就不高了", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:51:21.750000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510928782675152956", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "# 命輪 密契配置", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T08:51:33.489000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510931320178610176", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "一樣也是撿垃圾\n所以鳥哥帶自己專跟孤羽之後 隊友帶任意SR或以上的銀鑰 強效即可\n這次密契有點講究\n因為是需要隊友補生存 (除非凱夠強)\n所以看隊伍盾位是溫還是鳥哥\n前者可以詛咒兔 或者可以詛咒兔跟白子二選一 (哪個刷的好選哪個)", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T09:01:38.477000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
