{"id": "1510932205243732028", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "最推薦1 3\n鳥哥沒3啟可以考慮4\n缺生存可以用2", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T09:05:09.493000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510932968158265355", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "# 打法\n\n覺醒安排：\n道中要覺凱 鳥哥\n可以存空間打精英以及王\n王關進去先覺醒 回合結束進空間再二覺\n在後面回合考慮開第三覺醒\n\n需要用到溫+4是想加速王關\n可以在凱開完超限之後補一個超限給他 讓他第二發超限可以早一點開出來", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T09:08:11.386000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-01T09:28:28.084000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
{"id": "1510934216018231398", "channel_id": "1510692581120409760", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "打法跟上面差不多 都是凱單核\n||在覺醒之後盡量多打他的牌 號令觸手攻擊累積反擊\n不要在回合開始就先開靜海\n並建議從第二關道中開始就先開凱超限||←上面打法有提到的\n在此前提下 鳥哥覺醒後可以選敵方輸出意圖比較多的回合打出鳥哥黑羽(0算) 補充傷害 加速道中\n\n賣卡：\n掛件的打防 卡手的技能\n例如鳥哥3算 艾瑞卡打擊", "timestamp": "2026-06-01T09:13:08.899000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-01T09:21:44.296000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510692581120409760", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "AA凱刻斯", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179755759763526", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
